translate spanish d7b_e51e0ee3:

    # Zt "A girl like her is a rarity in these lands."
    Zt "Una chica como ella es una rareza en estas tierras."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:1999
translate spanish d7b_e786e02c:

    # Zt "She will make a great impression on my future guests."
    Zt "Causará una gran impresión a mis futuros invitados."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2002
translate spanish d7b_8348f35c:

    # Z "You were singing a song before I came in."
    Z "Estabas cantando una canción antes de que yo entrara."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2003
translate spanish d7b_f7c9c976:

    # Z "What language was that? I have not heard it before."
    Z "¿Qué lenguaje era ese? No lo he oído antes."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2006
translate spanish d7b_2640aacc:

    # E "Oh... it's...just a song my mother taught me, back when I was younger."
    E "Oh... es... sólo una canción que me enseñó mi madre, cuando era más joven."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2007
translate spanish d7b_27c6bd3a:

    # E "I only understand a few words of it... she always said it's a song from our home land."
    E "Sólo entiendo algunas palabras... ella siempre decía que era una canción de nuestra tierra natal."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2021
translate spanish d7b13_fa9db90b:

    # Z "What do you mean by your home land?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir con tu tierra natal?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2022
translate spanish d7b13_da8ef394:

    # Z "Were you born outside of Egypt?"
    Z "¿Naciste fuera de Egipto?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2025
translate spanish d7b13_34ffa30c:

    # E "Oh no, I was born here, somewhere in the north west of the region."
    E "Oh no, yo nací aquí, en algún lugar del noroeste de la región."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2026
translate spanish d7b13_9dac4e4e:

    # E "But my mother told me that the song is important for our people's history."
    E "Pero mi madre me dijo que la canción era importante para la historia de nuestro pueblo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2030
translate spanish d7b13_9cbf3902:

    # E "She made sure to teach it to me, like her mother taught it to her..."
    E "Se aseguró de enseñármela, como su madre se lo enseñó a ella..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2031
translate spanish d7b13_8e43e1f5:

    # E "...said it was important that we don't forget where we come from originally."
    E "... dijo que era importante que no olvidáramos de dónde venimos originalmente."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2034
translate spanish d7b13_208376ca:

    # Z "Where are these lands? Did your people come here before your mother was born?"
    Z "¿Dónde están esas tierras? ¿Vino tu gente aquí antes de que naciera tu madre?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2037
translate spanish d7b13_dafd3b22:

    # E "She said that it was a place far up north of Europe, as far as you can go, and that no one else came from there since the skies turned red..."
    E "Dice que era un lugar muy al norte de Europa, hasta donde se puede llegar, y que nadie más vino de allí desde que los cielos se volvieron rojos..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2038
translate spanish d7b13_5e2a1410:

    # E "...but that maybe one day we will return to those lands."
    E "... pero que tal vez un día volvamos a esas tierras."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2041
translate spanish d7b13_d2cb54ea:

    # Z "It has been many centuries since then."
    Z "Han pasado muchos siglos desde entonces."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2044
translate spanish d7b13_562fc21e:

    # E "For a long time after the war, they say there was a village, right here in Egypt, where the language of the song was commonly known and used."
    E "Durante mucho tiempo después de la guerra, dicen que había un pueblo, aquí mismo en Egipto, donde se conocía y se utilizaba la lengua de la canción."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2047
translate spanish d7b13_532d7919:

    # E "But eventually... that place was raided, and everything changed."
    E "Pero finalmente... ese lugar fue asaltado, y todo cambió."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2048
translate spanish d7b13_ae095fa5:

    # E "She always painted a picture of how it looked there, based on the tales."
    E "Ella siempre pintaba una imagen de cómo era allí, basándose en los cuentos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2051
translate spanish d7b13_e80d9ac2:

    # E "Tales of frozen lakes, so frozen that you can even walk on them."
    E "Cuentos de lagos congelados, tan congelados que incluso se podía caminar sobre ellos"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2054
translate spanish d7b13_d2af37e0:

    # E "Then there are mountains, and a blue sky that pierces through it and stretches across the horizon."
    E "Luego aparecen las montañas, y un cielo azul que lo atraviesa y se extiende por el horizonte."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2057
translate spanish d7b13_398ec638:

    # E "The air is very cold, not warm like here, and there is snow, as far as the eyes can see."
    E "El aire es muy frío, no cálido como aquí, y hay nieve, hasta donde alcanza la vista."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2058
translate spanish d7b13_d6ed9c04:

    # E "Have you ever seen snow, Master?"
    E "¿Has visto alguna vez la nieve, Amo?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2059
translate spanish d7b13_beab494a:

    # Z "I have, but only in one of the Zones I visited."
    Z "Yo sí, pero sólo en una de las Zonas que visité."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2060
translate spanish d7b13_c046dbea:

    # Z "It was impure... and toxic."
    Z "Era impuro... y tóxico."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2061
translate spanish d7b13_54d5bc6d:

    # E "My mother said that the snow in our land is white and clean."
    E "Mi madre decía que la nieve en nuestra tierra era blanca y limpia."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2062
translate spanish d7b13_2e3109bc:

    # E "She said it often falls from the sky, and that it feels funny when it falls on your tongue. This is what she was told."
    E "Decía que a menudo caía del cielo, y que tenía una sensación extraña cuando caía en la lengua. Esto es lo que la dijeron."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2065
translate spanish d7b13_5dab0987:

    # E "And even though we were never there, and never crossed the sea up North..."
    E "Y aunque nunca estuvimos allí, ni cruzamos el mar del Norte..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2066
translate spanish d7b13_44de1c20:

    # E "...I can imagine it very well... being there."
    E "... puedo imaginármelo muy bien...  estando allí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2070
translate spanish d7b13_7329681e:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2073
translate spanish d7b13_382e3b27:

    # E "I'm sorry for rambling, Master..."
    E "Siento haber divagado, Amo..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2074
translate spanish d7b13_6482fcf7:

    # E "I just sometimes can't help thinking about it."
    E "Es que a veces no puedo evitar pensar en ello."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2077
translate spanish d7b13_fa9db90b_1:

    # Z "What do you mean by your home land?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir con tu tierra natal?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2078
translate spanish d7b13_da8ef394_1:

    # Z "Were you born outside of Egypt?"
    Z "¿Naciste fuera de Egipto?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2081
translate spanish d7b13_2111115c:

    # E "No, I was born in these lands, somewhere in the north west."
    E "No, nací en estas tierras, en algún lugar del noroeste."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2082
translate spanish d7b13_b2c42b7b:

    # E "My mother told me that the song is important for our people's history."
    E "Mi madre me dijo que la canción era importante para la historia de nuestro pueblo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2085
translate spanish d7b13_9cbf3902_1:

    # E "She made sure to teach it to me, like her mother taught it to her..."
    E "Se aseguró de enseñármela, como su madre se lo enseñó a ella..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2086
translate spanish d7b13_804b97db:

    # E "...said it was important that we don't forget where we come from."
    E "... dijo que era importante que no olvidáramos de dónde venimos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2089
translate spanish d7b13_0a5e0fef:

    # E "But that was a long time ago."
    E "Pero eso fue hace mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2090
translate spanish d7b13_02a2af30:

    # E "It shouldn't concern you, Master."
    E "No debería preocuparte, amo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2096
translate spanish d7b13_de4ee3fe:

    # Z "The song sounded very comforting."
    Z "La canción sonaba muy reconfortante."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2099
translate spanish d7b13_863e0680:

    # E "I... don't know if everyone sang it like this."
    E "Yo... no sé si todo el mundo la cantaba así."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2102
translate spanish d7b13_2bc6c1cc:

    # E "But she did, back then... when she was trying to comfort me."
    E "Pero ella lo hacía, en aquel entonces... cuando trataba de consolarme."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2105
translate spanish d7b13_2a8e5b9a:

    # E "But enough about me, it's just a song after all."
    E "Pero basta de hablar de mí, al fin y al cabo es sólo una canción."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2106
translate spanish d7b13_7db11111:

    # Z "It is not just a song for you."
    Z "No es sólo una canción para ti."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2109
translate spanish d7b13_5e486cf3:

    # Z "You said she tried to comfort you?"
    Z "¿Dijiste que ella trató de consolarte?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2112
translate spanish d7b13_28e9918b:

    # E "We didn't..."
    E "No lo hicimos..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2115
translate spanish d7b13_df0effd4:

    # "You can see that it is difficult for her to talk about this."
    "Puedes ver que le resulta difícil hablar de esto."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2118
translate spanish d7b13_c2a6df15:

    # E "Not every Master is like you."
    E "No todos los Amos son como tú."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2121
translate spanish d7b13_b1408906:

    # E "My first master wasn't as benevolent."
    E "Mi primer Amo no era tan benévolo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2124
translate spanish d7b13_167c6111:

    # E "Back then, I did not understand why he would treat me like he did."
    E "Por aquel entonces, no entendía por qué me trataba así."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2125
translate spanish d7b13_a81fb3cd:

    # E "We were always very fearful when he would come home, because even though we did everything he asked us to do, it was never enough."
    E "Siempre teníamos mucho miedo cuando volvía a casa, porque aunque hacíamos todo lo que nos pedía, nunca era suficiente."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2128
translate spanish d7b13_8766b0fe:

    # E "Every time he left, I knew that the next time I would see him, his mood would still be just as dark."
    E "Cada vez que se iba, sabía que la próxima vez que lo viera, su humor seguiría siendo igual de oscuro."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2129
translate spanish d7b13_a161d18b:

    # E "I was feeling helpless and there seemed to be no solution to our misery."
    E "Me sentía impotente y no parecía haber solución a nuestra miseria."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2132
translate spanish d7b13_16cb8c9f:

    # E "That is when she would sing to me, telling stories about those far off lands."
    E "Entonces ella me cantaba, contándome historias sobre aquellas tierras lejanas."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2133
translate spanish d7b13_3cd4a291:

    # E "Tales of conquered adversity and proud people. It made things more bearable."
    E "Historias de adversidades vencidas y de personas orgullosas. Hizo que las cosas fueran más llevaderas."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2136
translate spanish d7b13_e7eda73a:

    # E "But I didn't have it so bad for very long."
    E "Pero no lo tuve tan mal durante mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2139
translate spanish d7b13_ad0c81ec:

    # E "When I was sold to someone in this city, things changed."
    E "Cuando me vendieron a alguien en esta ciudad, las cosas cambiaron."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2140
translate spanish d7b13_73fb470e:

    # E "I have had it much better, all things considered."
    E "Me ha ido mucho mejor, teniendo en cuenta todas las cosas."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2141
translate spanish d7b13_ad19ee7b:

    # E "I am still a slave; it's all I know anyway. But even someone like me knows the difference between a good and a bad owner."
    E "Sigo siendo una esclava; es todo lo que sé de todos modos. Pero incluso alguien como yo conoce la diferencia entre un buen y un mal dueño."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2144
translate spanish d7b13_9a0eab4e:

    # E "And sometimes the Mistress had special requests."
    E "Y a veces la Ama tenía peticiones especiales."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2147
translate spanish d7b13_dd04bdff:

    # E "But she was more predictable, and I didn't have fear anymore."
    E "Pero ella era más predecible, y ya no tenía miedo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2148
translate spanish d7b13_95c5bc0d:

    # E "I still keep singing the song, but it has a different meaning now."
    E "Todavía sigo cantando la canción, pero ahora tiene un significado diferente."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2154
translate spanish d7b13_b9b303c8:

    # Z "It's indeed a pretty song."
    Z "En efecto, es una bonita canción."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2157
translate spanish d7b13_fbd84598:

    # E "My previous Mistress liked it too, if it pleases you I can keep signing it for you Master."
    E "A mi anterior Ama también le gustaba, si te complace puedo haciéndolo para para ti Amo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2160
translate spanish d7b13_53eddf47:

    # Z "Your previous Mistress? You mean the Queen?"
    Z "¿Tu anterior Ama? ¿Te refieres a la Reina?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2163
translate spanish d7b13_d2f1469b:

    # E "Yes Master. She was strict but fair, much like you..."
    E "Sí, Amo. Era estricta pero justa, como tú..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2166
translate spanish d7b13_e49be26d:

    # E "...although she had some \"special\" requests from time to time..."
    E "... aunque de vez en cuando tenía algunas peticiones \"especiales\"..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2170
translate spanish d7b13_470f9dec:

    # Z "What meaning? Do you still want to be free?"
    Z "¿Qué sentido tiene? ¿Aún quieres ser libre?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2173
translate spanish d7b13_7329681e_1:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2174
translate spanish d7b13_5d8857da:

    # "She pauses, seemingly surprised about your question..."
    "Se detiene, aparentemente sorprendida por tu pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2177
translate spanish d7b13_2e44739a:

    # E "I've never been asked that question before."
    E "Nunca me habían hecho esa pregunta."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2180
translate spanish d7b13_fb0be229:

    # E "It never crossed my mind, really."
    E "Nunca se me pasó por la cabeza, la verdad."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2181
translate spanish d7b13_0e9c1757:

    # E "My mother and I grew up as servants. She had no memory of things being any different before, from the stories of her mother."
    E "Mi madre y yo crecimos como sirvientes. Ella no recordaba que las cosas fueran diferentes antes, por los relatos de su madre."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2184
translate spanish d7b13_4b0e5fdf:

    # E "But I don't mind how things turned out in the end."
    E "Pero no me importa cómo han acabado las cosas al final."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2185
translate spanish d7b13_ce175d13:

    # E "I would not know how to live for myself, and being here, I don't know that I want to."
    E "No sabría vivir por mí misma, y estando aquí, no sé si quiero hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2186
translate spanish d7b13_0c357620:

    # E "And I have not been serving you for long, but you have treated me fairly from the beginning, gave me my own space, and have been very kind."
    E "Y no llevo mucho tiempo sirviéndote, pero me has tratado con justicia desde el principio, me has dado mi propio espacio y has sido muy amable."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2189
translate spanish d7b13_1c1bab6f:

    # E "I can understand why the girls like living with you..."
    E "Puedo entender que a las chicas les guste vivir contigo..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2192
translate spanish d7b13_29022c0b:

    # E "...and I hope I can repay you adequately for your favour."
    E "... y espero poder devolverle adecuadamente tu favor."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2197
translate spanish d7b13_44d8e00a:

    # Z "You say she was much like me, hm?"
    Z "¿Dices que ella se parece mucho a mí?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2200
translate spanish d7b13_f365c1ac:

    # E "Yes Master. I have not been serving you for long, but you have given me clear rules from the start, told me how things are, and treated me fairly."
    E "Sí, Amo. No llevo mucho tiempo sirviéndote, pero me has dado reglas claras desde el principio, me has dicho cómo son las cosas y me has tratado con justicia."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2203
translate spanish d7b13_f7798073:

    # E "I can rest well at night, knowing this."
    E "Puedo descansar bien por la noche, sabiendo esto."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2207
translate spanish d7b13_f1ce4bf7:

    # Z "Tell me about the Mistresses special requests."
    Z "Háblame de las peticiones especiales de la Señora."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2210
translate spanish d7b13_620f9254:

    # E "Whenever her orders were going to be special or even confusing, she would hold up her hand in a way."
    E "Siempre que sus órdenes iban a ser especiales o incluso confusas, levantaba la mano de alguna manera."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2213
translate spanish d7b13_80302a54:

    # E "She would want me to come over without saying a word... feel my mouth... and whisper her orders to me... reminding me of my place."
    E "Ella querría que me acercara sin decir una palabra... palpar mi boca... y susurrarme sus órdenes... recordándome mi lugar."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2220
translate spanish d7b13_4ec91107:

    # E "...?"
    E "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2223
translate spanish d7b13_f2e09263:

    # Z "Like this?"
    Z "¿Así?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2226
translate spanish d7b13_c1cad2d1:

    # E "Yes, Master... Like this."
    E "Sí, Amo... Así."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2229
translate spanish d7b13_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2230
translate spanish d7b13_7fb8333a:

    # "You look at her expectingly..."
    "La miras con expectación..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2233
translate spanish d7b13_7329681e_2:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2236
translate spanish d7b13_7329681e_3:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2237
translate spanish d7b13_4e3db195:

    # Z "Hmm..."
    Z "Hmm..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2242
translate spanish d7b13_78e901c4:

    # Zw "You are the most beautiful maid in this city."
    Zw "Eres la criada más hermosa de esta ciudad."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2243
translate spanish d7b13_2021b864:

    # Zw "I think showing that to my future guests would be the right thing to do..."
    Zw "Creo que mostrarla a mis futuros invitados sería lo correcto..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2244
translate spanish d7b13_643124cd:

    # Zw "What do you think?"
    Zw "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2247
translate spanish d7b13_7329681e_4:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2250
translate spanish d7b13_e717ebe0:

    # Zw "I think that's a yes."
    Zw "Creo que eso es un sí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2253
translate spanish d7b13_dab9a105:

    # Zw "It will be simple. Whenever I give you the signal, you will quietly come to me. No matter what you're doing at the moment."
    Zw "Será sencillo. Cuando te dé la señal, vendrás tranquilamente hacia mí. No importa lo que estés haciendo en ese momento."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2256
translate spanish d7b13_6c3fe723:

    # Zw "It's a discrete solution, and allows me to not have to raise my voice."
    Zw "Es una solución discreta, y me permitirá no tener que levantar la voz."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2265
translate spanish d7b13_8b9cb198:

    # Zw "You can sit down again."
    Zw "Puedes sentarte de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2268
translate spanish d7b13_132f802e:

    # "She follows your orders..."
    "Ella obedece tus órdenes..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2274
translate spanish d7b13_0c7fc798:

    # Zw "From now on, whenever I raise my hand, you will come to me... without a sound."
    Zw "A partir de ahora, cada vez que levante la mano, vendrás a mí... sin hacer ruido."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2277
translate spanish d7b13_6b774a15:

    # Zw "And your head will stay in my hand until I give you your task, which you will execute without delay."
    Zw "Y tu cabeza permanecerá en mi mano hasta que te dé tu tarea, que ejecutarás sin demora."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2280
translate spanish d7b13_80d2d88e:

    # Zw "I want to show everyone that this beautiful maid belongs to me."
    Zw "Quiero mostrar a todos que esta hermosa sirvienta me pertenece."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2283
translate spanish d7b13_8ab0d9a3:

    # E "{i}*licking*"
    E "{i}*lamiendo*"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2286
translate spanish d7b13_7e93bd6a:

    # Zw "Good slave."
    Zw "Buens esclava."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2295
translate spanish d7b13_62f32059:

    # Zw "That's enough."
    Zw "Eso es suficiente."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2298
translate spanish d7b13_37f6e4d0:

    # "She sits back down..."
    "Se vuelve a sentar..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2307
translate spanish d7b13_e1fd8e00:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c]?"
    S "¿[persistent.dad!c]?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2310
translate spanish d7b13_1ae8cb27:

    # S "There you are..."
    S "Ahí estás..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2311
translate spanish d7b13_dcc54c6f:

    # "She walks up to you..."
    "Se acerca a ti..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2314
translate spanish d7b13_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2315
translate spanish d7b13_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2316
translate spanish d7b13_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2317
translate spanish d7b13_4b5a9d52:

    # Z "Yes?"
    Z "¿Sí?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2320
translate spanish d7b13_3e9b06f0:

    # S "[persistent.mom!c] said I have to go and buy groceries."
    S "[persistent.mom!c] dice que tengo que ir a comprar víveres."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2323
translate spanish d7b13_c117bf03:

    # Z "Such a tragedy."
    Z "Qué tragedia."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2326
translate spanish d7b13_92b8e2b7:

    # S "You know I hate it."
    S "Sabes que lo odio."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2329
translate spanish d7b13_871729f9:

    # S "Emilia knows best what we need to buy."
    S "Emilia sabe mejor que nadie lo que hay que comprar."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2330
translate spanish d7b13_72e71aa6:

    # S "Can I have her for a while?"
    S "¿Puedo tenerla un rato?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2333
translate spanish d7b13_07fd2901:

    # Z "Sure, we were done anyway."
    Z "Claro, de todos modos ya habíamos terminado."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2336
translate spanish d7b13_87546855:

    # E "See you soon, Master."
    E "Hasta pronto, Amo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2338
translate spanish d7b13_fea803ea:

    # Z "Well, this has been interesting, but we should get back to make something of today."
    Z "Bueno, esto ha sido interesante, pero deberíamos volver para hacer algo con el día de hoy."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2341
translate spanish d7b13_87546855_1:

    # E "See you soon, Master."
    E "Hasta pronto, Amo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2348
translate spanish d7b13_154dd411:

    # "The three of you leave the room and part ways."
    "Los tres salís de la habitación y os separáis."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2350
translate spanish d7b13_a9614db4:

    # "The two of you leave the room and part ways."
    "Los dos salís de la habitación y os separáis."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2359
translate spanish d7c_f7a8ee06:

    # "You reach the market. The weather is nice and people are strolling around and having a good time."
    "Llegas al mercado. Hace buen tiempo y la gente pasea y se divierte."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2360
translate spanish d7c_f1fcea02:

    # "As you look for things to buy, you and [W] stop by Igor's stall..."
    "Mientras buscáis cosas para comprar, tú y [W] os detenéis en el puesto de Igor..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2363
translate spanish d7c_e6d5bbf0:

    # C "I'm serious, the legates are heading out tonight."
    C "Lo digo en serio, los legados salen esta noche."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2364
translate spanish d7c_2016e967:

    # C "I wish I could stay, but I have to accompany them."
    C "Ojalá pudiera quedarme, pero tengo que acompañarles."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2367
translate spanish d7c_86b98d5a:

    # W "This sounds great, Igor. I'm so happy for you!"
    W "Esto suena muy bien, Igor. ¡Me alegro mucho por ti!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2370
translate spanish d7c_b6ef9471:

    # W "I guess the lonely nights are over then, right?"
    W "Supongo que las noches solitarias se han acabado, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2373
translate spanish d7c_d4254275:

    # Ig "Haha, you could say."
    Ig "Jajaja, se podría decir."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2374
translate spanish d7c_3234ab05:

    # Ig "But merchant always spends lonely nights with camels even so."
    Ig "Pero el comerciante siempre pasa las noches solitarias con los camellos incluso así."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2377
translate spanish d7c_93035f04:

    # W "So, what exactly does she do for a living?"
    W "Entonces, ¿a qué se dedica exactamente?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2378
translate spanish d7c_abc1c866:

    # Zt "[W] looks so young when she does herself up like in the old days."
    Zt "[W] Parece tan joven cuando se arregla como en los viejos tiempos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2379
translate spanish d7c_1acc6f2a:

    # Zt "I would love to let her know just how she makes me feel right now, but..."
    Zt "Me encantaría hacerle saber cómo me hace sentir ahora mismo, pero..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2382
translate spanish d7c_76a2c228:

    # Zt "I guess now is not the time."
    Zt "Supongo que ahora no es el momento."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2385
translate spanish d7c_a1ef524f:

    # Zt "Even when we don't talk, Kateryna reaches for my arm every time we meet."
    Zt "Incluso cuando no hablamos, Kateryna me coge del brazo cada vez que nos encontramos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2388
translate spanish d7c_b93c3348:

    # Zt "Not that I'm complaining..."
    Zt "No es que me queje..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2397
translate spanish d7c_83b7a7eb:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2400
translate spanish d7c_6ad09c50:

    # "They keep on chatting..."
    "Ellos siguen charlando..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2401
translate spanish d7c_f34cf279:

    # Zt "I love Igor, but now we're just wasting time..."
    Zt "Adoro a Igor, pero ahora sólo estamos perdiendo el tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2404
translate spanish d7c_f6c35e2d:

    # Zt "..."
    Zt "..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2407
translate spanish d7c_352779b4:

    # Zt "Wait, isn't that..."
    Zt "Espera, esos no son..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2408
translate spanish d7c_1c368aab:

    # Z "Hey [W], guess who's here."
    Z "Ey [W], adivina quién está aquí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2411
translate spanish d7c_3ca771e7:

    # W "Mhh?"
    W "¿Mhh?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2414
translate spanish d7c_5f3dbf23:

    # W "Kateryna? Hello girl..."
    W "¿Kateryna? Hola chica..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2415
translate spanish d7c_3e29ec53:

    # Z "Not what I meant...Look behind you, the woman in green."
    Z "No es lo que quería decir... Mira detrás de ti, la mujer de verde."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2418
translate spanish d7c_ade8c88f:

    # W "Huh?"
    W "¿Eh?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2419
translate spanish d7c_3a48a984:

    # W "No way!"
    W "¡No puede ser!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2422
translate spanish d7c_243ef026:

    # W "It's Rabiah!"
    W "¡Es Rabiah!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2425
translate spanish d7c_edcab653:

    # W "Kateryna, Igor, it was nice to speak to you, but... that's my sister. I have to go."
    W "Kateryna, Igor, ha sido un placer hablar con vosotros, pero... es mi hermana. Tengo que irme."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2428
translate spanish d7c_8f9217ef:

    # W "[persistent.player_name!c], please come with me."
    W "[persistent.player_name!c], por favor, ven conmigo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2431
translate spanish d7c_59df2798:

    # "You say goodbye to Kateryna and Igor and follow your wife..."
    "Te despides de Kateryna y de Igor y sigues a tu mujer..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2432
translate spanish d7c_72a01ceb:

    # W "Sister!"
    W "¡Hermana!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2433
translate spanish d7c_925e105f:

    # Ra "[W]?"
    Ra "¿[W]?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2434
translate spanish d7c_6841ced6:

    # W "It's good to see you; I didn't expect you here!"
    W "Me alegro de verte; ¡no te esperaba aquí!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2435
translate spanish d7c_7192f7ef:

    # Ra "Come here; let me hug you."
    Ra "Ven aquí; deja que te abrace."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2438
translate spanish d7c_dc6985be:

    # W "So you finally moved back?"
    W "¿Así que finalmente has vuelto a mudarte?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2439
translate spanish d7c_9d5cff18:

    # Ra "{i}*chuckles* Yes, we did."
    Ra "{i}*risilla* Sí, lo hicimos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2442
translate spanish d7c_c56e3af0:

    # W "You have been in the village for so long..."
    W "Llevas tanto tiempo en el pueblo..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2445
translate spanish d7c_f6053249:

    # W "I really missed having you around."
    W "Realmente echaba de menos tenerte cerca."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2448
translate spanish d7c_89ac67ef:

    # Ra "Aww, don't be like that. I am back now, aren't I?"
    Ra "Ohh, no seas así. Ya he vuelto, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2451
translate spanish d7c_332af1ba:

    # "They give each other a brief kiss..."
    "Ellas se dan un breve beso..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2454
translate spanish d7c_adc4002a:

    # W "So... how are you all doing?"
    W "Y... ¿cómo os va a todos?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2455
translate spanish d7c_4eaf6916:

    # Z "Hello Omar, long time no see."
    Z "Hola Omar, cuánto tiempo sin verte."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2458
translate spanish d7c_cdb76b2f:

    # Zt "I'd forgotten his limp handshake."
    Zt "Había olvidado su flojo apretón de manos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2459
translate spanish d7c_9d6289c1:

    # Zt "It's like I'm holding a wet sausage..."
    Zt "Es como si sostuviera una salchicha húmeda..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2462
translate spanish d7c_e74f7bd7:

    # Om "Hello [persistent.player_name], it's been a while."
    Om "Hola [persistent.player_name], hace tiempo que no te veo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2465
translate spanish d7c_f38b9654:

    # Z "How are you holding up? Did you move your business to the city or did you leave it in the village?"
    Z "¿Cómo lo llevas? ¿Has trasladado tu negocio a la ciudad o lo has dejado en la aldea?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2468
translate spanish d7c_d4fc97e8:

    # Om "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Of course I moved it here. It will be harder to keep a connection with the outside tribes from now on, but I should manage."
    Om "{i}*risilla*{/i} Por supuesto que la he trasladado aquí. A partir de ahora será más difícil mantener la conexión con las tribus del exterior, pero debería arreglármelas."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2469
translate spanish d7c_ca444436:

    # Om "How is working for the Queen going for you?"
    Om "¿Cómo te va el trabajo para la Reina?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2472
translate spanish d7c_9a787766:

    # Z "I don't work for the Queen, I work {i}with{/i} her."
    Z "No trabajo para la Reina, trabajo {i}con{/i} ella."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2473
translate spanish d7c_7b128c40:

    # Z "But tell me, how's the family doing? Kian and Nadia must be excited to live here now."
    Z "Pero dime, ¿cómo está la familia? Kian y Nadia deben estar contentos de vivir aquí ahora."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2476
translate spanish d7c_7c7bf584:

    # Om "They are. The kids growing up is one of the main reasons Rabiah insisted on moving back here."
    Om "Lo han hecho. El crecimiento de los niños es una de las principales razones por las que Rabiah insistió en volver aquí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2477
translate spanish d7c_dd688606:

    # Om "I'm a bit worried about little Nadia, to be honest. The city could give her some... improper ideas."
    Om "Estoy un poco preocupado por la pequeña Nadia, para ser sincero. La ciudad podría darle algunas ideas... impropias."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2480
translate spanish d7c_c4ef76b3:

    # Om "She's growing up fast as well, that one. She has been behaving differently recently..."
    Om "Esa niña también está creciendo muy rápido. Últimamente se comporta de forma diferente..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2483
translate spanish d7c_4db57aaf:

    # Ra "She's just going through a phase at the moment."
    Ra "Sólo está pasando por una fase en este momento."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2484
translate spanish d7c_f8797256:

    # Ra "And you seem to have lost track of her again. We should go and look for her."
    Ra "Y parece que has vuelto a perder el rastro de ella. Deberíamos ir a buscarla."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2485
translate spanish d7c_66efcb63:

    # Ra "[W] tells me the market isn't always safe."
    Ra "[W] me dijo que el mercado no siempre es seguro."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2488
translate spanish d7c_47eb33df:

    # Ra "Hello, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ra "Hola, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2491
translate spanish d7c_8addbb79:

    # Z "Hey [Ra], it's been too long."
    Z "Ey [Ra], ha pasado mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2494
translate spanish d7c_0fb5bc18:

    # W "[persistent.player_name!c], is it okay if [Ra] and I go and look for Nadia?"
    W "[persistent.player_name!c], ¿te parece bien que [Ra] y yo vayamos a buscar a Nadia?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2497
translate spanish d7c_30a344be:

    # Z "Sure, we will wait here for you."
    Z "Claro, os esperaremos aquí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2500
translate spanish d7c_6e5b0211:

    # "The sisters wander off, still chatting..."
    "Las hermanas se alejan, todavía charlando..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2503
translate spanish d7c_bc020384:

    # Om "You are really lucky [W] found you, [persistent.player_name]. It looks like your wife never ages."
    Om "Tienes mucha suerte de que [W] te haya encontrado, [persistent.player_name]. Parece que tu mujer nunca envejece."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2504
translate spanish d7c_a1297331:

    # Om "I see she likes to dress quite liberally too. {i}*laughs awkwardly*"
    Om "Veo que a ella también le gusta vestirse con bastante libertad. {i}*se ríe incómodo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2509
translate spanish d7c_bdf0528c:

    # Z "Hm, you think so?"
    Z "Umm, ¿crees que sí?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2512
translate spanish d7c_af948f8e:

    # Z "Let me tell you something."
    Z "Deja que te cuente algo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2515
translate spanish d7c_f9abf020:

    # Zw "I was going to ignore your attempt at belittling my rank, but now you're also telling me that finding her was just dumb luck, and that doesn't sit well with me."
    Zw "Iba a ignorar tu intento de menospreciar mi rango, pero ahora también me dices que encontrarla fue pura suerte, y eso no me gusta."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2516
translate spanish d7c_8908b622:

    # Zw "I am not lucky, I work for my success."
    Zw "No tuve suerte, trabajé por mi éxito."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2517
translate spanish d7c_4914a9c2:

    # Zw "My wife didn't find me, I chose her."
    Zw "Mi mujer no me encontró, yo la elegí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2518
translate spanish d7c_0c3e210b:

    # Zw "I make her feel appreciated. She likes to take care of herself, for herself and for me."
    Zw "La hago sentir apreciada. Le gusta cuidarse, para ella misma y para mí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2521
translate spanish d7c_ea031eb8:

    # "You tap him on the chest..."
    "Le das un golpecito en el pecho..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2524
translate spanish d7c_3824364b:

    # Zw "If you must be obnoxious, I suggest you keep your comments to yourself if you want us to get along."
    Zw "Si tienes que ser odioso, te sugiero que te guardes tus comentarios si quieres que nos llevemos bien."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2525
translate spanish d7c_eb4e76a0:

    # Zw "Just so we understand one another."
    Zw "Sólo para que nos entendamos."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2526
translate spanish d7c_5178d161:

    # Om "S-sure, we can agree on this..."
    Om "C...claro, podemos estar de acuerdo en esto..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2530
translate spanish d7c_0a52e132:

    # Z "She's great, I agree. In all these years, she's always been the perfect wife, in bed too, even now."
    Z "Ella está muy bien, estoy de acuerdo. En todos estos años, siempre ha sido la esposa perfecta, también en la cama, incluso ahora."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2531
translate spanish d7c_e7038bc1:

    # Z "But your wife isn't bad either, I don't know why you're so jealous."
    Z "Pero tu mujer tampoco está mal, no sé por qué estás tan celoso."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2532
translate spanish d7c_5f1a84f0:

    # Z "I remember her being a wildcat when I was with her. Surely that hasn't changed much?"
    Z "Recuerdo que era una fiera cuando estaba con ella. Seguro que eso no ha cambiado mucho."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2535
translate spanish d7c_c1419163:

    # "He looks uncomfortable..."
    "El parece incómodo..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2536
translate spanish d7c_ccc45a3d:

    # Om "Oh, uh, yes, I guess."
    Om "Oh, eh, sí, supongo."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2539
translate spanish d7c_559b5f53:

    # Om "I don't really want to impose on her too much. We are not as young as we were, and I like to treat her with respect."
    Om "No quiero imponerle demasiado. Ya no somos tan jóvenes como antes, y me gusta tratarla con respeto."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2542
translate spanish d7c_de18f5d2:

    # Z "Ah, well, she does look a bit more relaxed, I guess, compared to the last time I saw her..."
    Z "Ah, bueno, parece un poco más relajada, supongo, en comparación con la última vez que la vi..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2543
translate spanish d7c_e65a570b:

    # Z "Even dresses much more conservatively than I remember, now that I notice."
    Z "Incluso viste de forma mucho más conservadora de lo que recordaba, ahora que me doy cuenta."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2544
translate spanish d7c_bff3306c:

    # Zt "Wimp."
    Zt "Blandengue."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2551
translate spanish d7c46_5219b0cd:

    # Z "Oh, look who's back."
    Z "Oh, mira quién ha vuelto."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2552
translate spanish d7c46_fabe7c84:

    # Ra "I told you I don't want you strolling around the market like that."
    Ra "Te dije que no quiero que te pasees así por el mercado."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2553
translate spanish d7c46_48b51cc6:

    # Ra "You've heard what happened to your cousins!"
    Ra "¡Has oído lo que les pasó a tus primas!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2554
translate spanish d7c46_3abac15b:

    # Na "Yeah, yeah, mother."
    Na "Sí, sí, madre."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2555
translate spanish d7c46_836780a6:

    # Na "One incident in a century, and suddenly everyone loses their shit."
    Na "Un incidente en un siglo, y de repente todo el mundo pierde la cabeza."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2558
translate spanish d7c46_5ec55d08:

    # "They come over..."
    "Ellas se acercan..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2559
translate spanish d7c46_15acbf3b:

    # Na "Damn! I haven't seen you in ages!"
    Na "¡Maldita sea! ¡Hace años que no te veo!"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2562
translate spanish d7c46_33d9c1ba:

    # Na "Hey uncle, good to see you."
    Na "Ey tío, me alegro de verte."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2563
translate spanish d7c46_62657960:

    # Z "Is that really you, little Nadia?"
    Z "¿Eres realmente tú, pequeña Nadia?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2564
translate spanish d7c46_f14d4c52:

    # Z "I almost didn't recognize you without your ponytails."
    Z "Casi no te reconozco sin tus coletas."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2565
translate spanish d7c46_532527a7:

    # Na "Those have been gone a long time now."
    Na "Hace ya mucho tiempo que esas se fueron."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2568
translate spanish d7c46_a9fdbe2b:

    # "You fistbump her..."
    "Le chocas el puño..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2571
translate spanish d7c46_19e527ec:

    # Na "You still remember me."
    Na "Todavía te acuerdas de mí."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2574
translate spanish d7c46_9504335e:

    # Z "Of course. Why would I forget my niece?"
    Z "Por supuesto. ¿Por qué iba a olvidar a mi sobrina?"

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2577
translate spanish d7c46_ddc5577d:

    # Na "I think we have a lot to catch up on."
    Na "Creo que tenemos mucho que ponernos al día."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2580
translate spanish d7c46_78a0ec63:

    # Na "Dad, tell mom I'm showing uncle something."
    Na "Papá, dile a mamá que le voy a enseñar algo al tío."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2581
translate spanish d7c46_ddf6525e:

    # Na "We'll be right back."
    Na "Volveremos enseguida."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2582
translate spanish d7c46_4c4a151f:

    # Om "Sure, I guess. Try to not do a-"
    Om "Claro, supongo. Intenta no hacer na..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2583
translate spanish d7c46_d04aff4f:

    # Na "Yeah yeah, I won't do anything weird, I know..."
    Na "Sí, sí, no haré nada raro, lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2586
translate spanish d7c46_fe8af19e:

    # "You separate from your respective families..."
    "Os separáis de vuestras respectivas familias..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2589
translate spanish d7c46_5cfbe0f5:

    # Na "I swear, if he would just get the stick out of his ass for a minute, we'd all be happier for it..."
    Na "Te juro que si se sacara el palo del culo un minuto, todos seríamos más felices por ello..."

# game/scripts/day7.rpy:2590
translate spanish d7c46_58b7b21e:

    # Na "But no, all he does is act like a whiny bore all day long. He even forbids me to go out and have fun, can you believe it?"
